---
// Achievements component
---

<section id="achievements" class="achievements">
	<div class="achievements-container">
		<h2 class="section-title fade-in" data-i18n="achievements.title">Logros</h2>
		<div class="achievements-grid stagger-children">
			<div class="achievement-card slide-in-up">
				<div class="achievement-icon">
					<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
						<path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5zM2 17l10 5 10-5M2 12l10 5 10-5"/>
					</svg>
				</div>
				<h3 class="achievement-title" data-i18n="achievements.ach1Title">Liderazgo Técnico</h3>
				<p class="achievement-description" data-i18n="achievements.ach1Desc">Lideré la gestión de cambios y sincronización con equipos de QA en proyectos empresariales.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="achievement-card slide-in-up">
				<div class="achievement-icon">
					<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
						<path d="M14 2H6c-1.1 0-1.99.9-1.99 2L4 20c0 1.1.89 2 1.99 2H18c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2V8l-6-6zm2 16H8v-2h8v2zm0-4H8v-2h8v2zm-3-5V3.5L18.5 9H13z"/>
					</svg>
				</div>
				<h3 class="achievement-title" data-i18n="achievements.ach2Title">Documentación Técnica</h3>
				<p class="achievement-description" data-i18n="achievements.ach2Desc">Elaboré manuales de usuario y técnicos completos para facilitar el mantenimiento del sistema.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="achievement-card slide-in-up">
				<div class="achievement-icon">
					<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
						<path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm-2 15l-5-5 1.41-1.41L10 14.17l7.59-7.59L19 8l-9 9z"/>
					</svg>
				</div>
				<h3 class="achievement-title" data-i18n="achievements.ach3Title">Metodología Ágil</h3>
				<p class="achievement-description" data-i18n="achievements.ach3Desc">Trabajé exitosamente bajo metodología SCRUM, participando activamente en sprints y retrospectivas.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="achievement-card slide-in-up">
				<div class="achievement-icon">
					<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
						<path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/>
					</svg>
				</div>
				<h3 class="achievement-title" data-i18n="achievements.ach4Title">Migración a Serverless</h3>
				<p class="achievement-description" data-i18n="achievements.ach4Desc">Migré exitosamente controladores a funciones serverless utilizando AWS Lambda.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	.achievements {
		padding: 6rem 2rem;
		background: transparent;
		position: relative;
	}

	.achievements-container {
		max-width: 1200px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	.section-title {
		font-size: 3rem;
		text-align: center;
		margin-bottom: 4rem;
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffffff 0%, #a8a8a8 100%);
		-webkit-background-clip: text;
		-webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
		background-clip: text;
		font-weight: 700;
		letter-spacing: -0.02em;
	}

	.achievements-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
		gap: 2rem;
	}

	.achievement-card {
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
		backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
		border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
		border-radius: 16px;
		padding: 2.5rem;
		text-align: center;
		transition: all 0.3s ease;
	}

	.achievement-card:hover {
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
		border-color: rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.4);
		transform: translateY(-5px);
		box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.2);
	}

	.achievement-icon {
		width: 70px;
		height: 70px;
		margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.2) 0%, rgba(118, 75, 162, 0.2) 100%);
		border-radius: 16px;
		color: #667eea;
	}

	.achievement-icon svg {
		width: 40px;
		height: 40px;
	}

	.achievement-title {
		font-size: 1.5rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		color: #ffffff;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.achievement-description {
		color: #b0b0b0;
		line-height: 1.6;
		font-size: 1rem;
	}

	/* Light Theme */
	:global([data-theme="light"]) .section-title {
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a1a 0%, #4a4a4a 100%);
		-webkit-background-clip: text;
		-webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
		background-clip: text;
	}

	:global([data-theme="light"]) .achievement-card {
		background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.03);
		border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
	}

	:global([data-theme="light"]) .achievement-card:hover {
		background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
		border-color: rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.3);
		box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.15);
	}

	:global([data-theme="light"]) .achievement-title {
		color: #1a1a1a;
	}

	:global([data-theme="light"]) .achievement-description {
		color: #444;
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.achievements {
			padding: 4rem 2rem;
		}

		.section-title {
			font-size: 2rem;
			margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
		}

		.achievements-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}
	}
</style>

